The paper discusses privacy and security challenges in fog computing, which are typically addressed in the computer security (cs.CR) and cybersecurity (cs.CY) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the practical application of fog computing in three case studies, which falls under the sub-categories of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), software engineering (cs.SE), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
